/gait difficulty)","guid":"cRUELC6cLCPh1FCq_jfu9Q","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"11","text":"Severidad enfermedad","guid":"jxXth03q_gOL8PWrhfrQug","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Correlación lineal con\\Nestadio Hoehn & Yahr","guid":"C1RGYdnfA7M9KVdKlMLJxA","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Correlación con dosis equivalente levodopa (LEDD)","guid":"0uq8bMz1zIPUGV52i-lLsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"11","text":"Hipotensión\\Nortostática","guid":"D_5ZG4V4uhTVC5N9eDprCA","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Presente >50% pacientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Exacerbada por levodopa y agonistas dopaminérgicos","guid":"G5b8ZEM_4itkMtXHUsXs6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"11","text":"Discinesias → pérdida equilibrio","guid":"LnlyQ9xWtW3rdaI6zQJLDA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"11","text":"Freezing of gait → caídas súbitas","guid":"OkSbxe7mtjXxhfvor5shqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"1","text":"Mortalidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Fractura cadera = mediador principal de mortalidad (no osteoporosis per se)","guid":"lnt30qvp6xM5kCZ3XR45Ng","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"Mortalidad 1 año post-fractura: ~2x vs sin fractura","guid":"IRHbNKBu5ZOq6jpyn2V6XA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"Mortalidad 30 días: aRR 1.11","guid":"MiR2Bw1O10FcT2JSRGJSPw","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"↑ Neumonía, ITU, sepsis nosocomial","guid":"xnzLE2pjaQGEilk1PaKzFA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"2. OSTEOPOROSIS EN PARKINSON\\N(\"Neuro-osteoporosis\")","guid":"Tm4ZMIrxlPrNF5gPBCEiDg","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Prevalencia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Mujeres: hasta 91%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Hombres: hasta 61%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Solo 4.1% diagnóstico previo a fractura","guid"